briefTitle: Prospective Radiologic Evaluation of Changes Following Fat Grafting
officialTitle: Prospective Radiologic Evaluation of Changes That Might Affect Breast Cancer Diagnosis Following Fat Grafting and Silicone Breast Implants
eligibilityCriteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* Women with silicone implants and fat grafting
